---
title: "Sequence Diyagramı 1: Onboarding ve Kariyer Önerisi"
---
sequenceDiagram
    actor User as Kullanıcı
    participant Home as HomePage
    participant Onboard as OnboardingWizard
    participant API as RecommendAPI<br/>(/api/recommend)
    participant DB as tracks.json
    participant LS as localStorage

    Note over User,LS: Uygulama Başlangıcı

    User->>Home: Uygulamayı Aç
    Home->>LS: storage.load()
    LS-->>Home: userData (surveyAnswers = null)
    Home->>Home: view = 'onboarding'
    Home->>Onboard: Render OnboardingWizard

    Note over User,Onboard: Anket Süreci (12 Soru)

    loop Her soru için (12 adet)
        Onboard->>User: Soruyu Göster (4 seçenek)
        User->>Onboard: Cevap Seç
        Onboard->>Onboard: answers[questionId] = value<br/>currentStep++
    end

    Note over Onboard,DB: Kariyer Önerisi Hesaplama

    Onboard->>API: POST /api/recommend {answers}
    API->>DB: tracks.json oku (15 kariyer yolu)
    DB-->>API: Tüm track verileri
    API->>API: scoreTracks(answers)<br/>- platform_preference analizi<br/>- interest_area eşleştirme<br/>- work_style puanlama<br/>- match_percentage hesapla
    API-->>Onboard: TrackRecommendation<br/>{trackId, trackTitle, confidence, reasons, alternatives[]}

    Onboard->>User: Öneri Ekranı Göster<br/>"Frontend Developer - %85 Uyum"<br/>Sebepler + Alternatifler
    User->>Onboard: "Yola Başla" tıkla
    Onboard->>Home: onComplete(recommendation)

    Note over Home,LS: Sonuç Kaydetme

    Home->>LS: storage.saveSurveyAnswers(answers)
    Home->>LS: storage.setRecommendedTrack(trackId)
    Home->>Home: view = 'dashboard'
    Home->>User: Dashboard + Roadmap Göster
